name: [LORA]Flat_Color
description:
When an image is colored in solid blocks of color, without shadows, highlights, or gradients. The image is "flat" in that there are little to no indications of depth.

This model works better on scenery than character,if you want a image with a well sketched girl , I wont recommend you to try this lora.
